caption:
The last thing that I think about before going to bed is my run the following morning. At night, I dream about becoming a champion one day and the hard work that I need to continue doing. After I wake up my day begins as soon as I put on my HOKA trainers and hit the road.

As soon as I start running, I have a great sense of freedom and wellbeing, and any anxiety that I sometimes feel from being autistic, disappears. You are now halfway through your #Bondi9Challenge. I hope that the challenge has been great for your health and wellness.

I believe in you. Come On 🤩🤩💪🏾
